<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isun kei ei lungsietna chuh,
 Thing hansedawla thuok dingin;
 Thagau suokcha ka hih theih nan,
 Gen sangin a lien zawi.

[V2]
 A lungsiet gen sangin a lien,
 A lungsiet gen sangin a lien;
 Isun kei ei lungsietna chu,
 Gen sangin a lien zawi.

[V3]
 2. Lungkhamna haksa a thawk chuh,
 Leh aw, ling lukhuk A khuk chuh;
 Kumkhawsawt a ka hinna din,
 Gen sangin a lien zawi.

[V4]
 3. Lalchutphah ma-ah ei ngetsak,
 Lalpa ah lungmuonna ka nei;
 A thisan lul mantam zie chuh,
 Gen sangin a lien zawi.

[V5]
 4. Ei naih tienga kipahna chuh,
 Lauhna a chawlhna ei piek chuh;
 Amah a kinepna chien tak,
 Gen sangin a lien zawi.</lyrics>
<title>MORE THAN TONGUE CAN TELL</title>
<hymn_number>108</hymn_number>
</song>